EGER)\n- `referee_rebate_lamports`, `referee_rebate_rate_bps` (INTEGER)\n- `created_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ)\n- **Unique constraint**: `(referee_wallet, round_id)` — idempotency guard, prevents double-counting earnings\n- **Indexes**: \n  - `idx_referral_earnings_referrer` on `(referrer_wallet, created_at)`\n  - `idx_referral_earnings_referee` on `(referee_wallet, created_at)`\n  - `idx_referral_earnings_round_id` on `round_id`\n\n#### `referral_claims`\n- `id` (UUID PK), `wallet` (TEXT), `amount_lamports` (BIGINT)\n- `status` (TEXT, defaults to `'pending'`, CHECK: 'pending'|'processing'|'completed'|'failed')\n- `tx_signature`, `error` (TEXT, nullable)\n- `requested_at`, `processed_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ)\n- **Indexes**:\n  - `idx_referral_claims_wallet` on `(wallet, requested_at)`\n  - `idx_referral_claims_status` (partial, WHERE status IN ('pending', 'processing'))\n\n#### `referral_kol_rates`\n- `wallet` (TEXT PK), `rate_bps` (INTEGER)\n- `set_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ)\n- **Purpose**: Override default referrer rate (default 1000 bps = 10%)\n\n#### `event_queue`\n- `id` (BIGSERIAL PK), `event_type` (TEXT), `payload` (JSONB)\n- `status` (TEXT, defaults 'pending', CHECK: pending|processing|completed|failed|dead)\n- `attempts`, `max_attempts` (INTEGER, default 3), `scheduled_at`, `started_at`, `completed_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ)\n- `error` (TEXT, nullable)\n- **Index**: `idx_event_queue_poll` (partial, WHERE status='pending') for worker scanning\n\n---\n\n## 3. Database Interface (`Db` type)\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts` (lines 206–419)\n\n### Referral Code Methods\n| Method | Input | Output | Notes |\n|--------|-------|--------|-------|\n| `insertReferralCode(wallet, code)` | string, string | Promise<ReferralCode> | Throws on duplicate wallet or code |\n| `getReferralCodeByWallet(wallet)` | string | Promise<ReferralCode \\| undefined> | Fetch player's current code |\n| `getReferralCodeByCode(code)` | string | Promise<ReferralCode \\| undefined> | Lookup referrer by code string |\n| `upsertReferralCode(wallet, code)` | string, string | Promise<ReferralCode> | INSERT ON CONFLICT UPDATE — replaces player's code |\n\n### Referral Link Methods\n| Method | Input | Output | Notes |\n|--------|-------|--------|-------|\n| `insertReferralLink(referrerWallet, refereeWallet)` | string, string | Promise<ReferralLink> | Throws on duplicate referee wallet |\n| `getReferralLinkByReferee(refereeWallet)` | string | Promise<ReferralLink \\| undefined> | Check if player has a referrer |\n| `getReferralLinksByReferrer(referrerWallet)` | string | Promise<ReferralLink[]> | Get all players referred by a wallet (ordered DESC by created_at) |\n\n### Referral Earnings & Stats\n| Method | Input | Output | Notes |\n|--------|-------|--------|-------|\n| `insertReferralEarning(params)` | Object (see below) | Promise<ReferralEarning> | Throws on duplicate (referee_wallet, round_id) — idempotency guard |\n| `getPendingBalance(wallet)` | string | Promise<string> | Lamports as string: sum earned (referrer) + sum rebate (referee) - claimed |\n| `getReferralEarnings(wallet, page, limit)` | string, number, number | Promise<{items, totalPages}> | Paginated earnings for wallet as referrer, newest first |\n| `getReferralStats(wallet)` | string | Promise<ReferralStats> | Summary: referredCount, activeCount (7-day), totalVolume, totalEarned, totalRebate, pendingLamports |\n\n### insertReferralEarning Parameters\n```typescript\n{\n  referrerWallet: string;\n  refereeWallet: string;\n  roundId: string;\n  gameType: string;\n  wagerLamports: number;\n  feeLamports: number;\n  referrerEarnedLamports: number;\n  referrerRateBps: number;\n  refereeRebateLamports: number;\n  refereeRebateRateBps: number;\n}\n```\n\n### Referral Claims Methods\n| Method | Input | Output | Notes |\n|--------|-------|--------|-------|\n| `insertReferralClaim(wallet, amountLamports)` | string, string | Promise<ReferralClaim> | Inserts with status='pending' |\n| `getReferralClaim(claimId)` | string | Promise<ReferralClaim \\| undefined> | Fetch by UUID for polling |\n| `updateClaimStatus(claimId, status, meta?)` | string, status, {txSignature?, error?} | Promise<ReferralClaim> | Updates status + optional tx_signature/error; auto-sets processed_at if completed/failed |\n\n### Rate Methods\n| Method | Input | Output | Notes |\n|--------|-------|--------|-------|\n| `getReferrerRate(wallet, defaultRateBps)` | string, number | Promise<number> | Checks `referral_kol_rates` first; falls back to default (typically 1000 bps) |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Type Definitions\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts` (lines 127–178)\n\n### ReferralCode\n```typescript\n{\n  id: number;\n  wallet: string;\n  code: string;\n  created_at: Date;\n  updated_at: Date;\n}\n```\n\n### ReferralLink\n```typescript\n{\n  id: number;\n  referrer_wallet: string;\n  referee_wallet: string;\n  created_at: Date;\n}\n```\n\n### ReferralEarning\n```typescript\n{\n  id: number;\n  referrer_wallet: string;\n  referee_wallet: string;\n  round_id: string;\n  game_type: string;\n  wager_lamports: number;        // normalized to number by normalizeReferralEarning()\n  fee_lamports: number;\n  referrer_earned_lamports: number;\n  referrer_rate_bps: number;\n  referee_rebate_lamports: number;\n  referee_rebate_rate_bps: number;\n  created_at: Date;\n}\n```\n\n### ReferralStats\n```typescript\n{\n  referred_count: number;           // total players referred\n  active_count: number;             // distinct players with earnings in last 7 days\n  total_volume_lamports: string;    // sum of wager_lamports (joined with referral_links)\n  total_earned_lamports: string;    // sum of referrer_earned_lamports\n  total_rebate_lamports: string;    // sum of referee_rebate_lamports\n  pending_lamports: string;         // earned + rebate - claimed\n}\n```\n\n### ReferralClaim\n```typescript\n{\n  id: string;                       // UUID\n  wallet: string;\n  amount_lamports: string;\n  status: \"pending\" | \"processing\" | \"completed\" | \"failed\";\n  tx_signature: string | null;\n  error: string | null;\n  requested_at: Date;\n  processed_at: Date | null;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. Normalization Pattern\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts` (lines 447–457)\n\nPostgres returns BIGINT as `number` or `string` depending on context. The `normalizeReferralEarning()` function explicitly converts all numeric fields to `number`:\n\n```typescript\nfunction normalizeReferralEarning(row: ReferralEarning): ReferralEarning {\n  return {\n    ...row,\n    wager_lamports: Number(row.wager_lamports),\n    fee_lamports: Number(row.fee_lamports),\n    referrer_earned_lamports: Number(row.referrer_earned_lamports),\n    referrer_rate_bps: Number(row.referrer_rate_bps),\n    referee_rebate_lamports: Number(row.referee_rebate_lamports),\n    referee_rebate_rate_bps: Number(row.referee_rebate_rate_bps),\n  };\n}\n```\n\nApplied in:\n- `insertReferralEarning()` (line 860)\n- `getReferralEarnings()` (line 901) — maps each item in results\n\n---\n\n## 6. Integration Point: Settlement\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts`\n\nWhen a round settles, the worker:\n1. For each player in the round, check `db.getReferralLinkByReferee(playerWallet)`\n2. If linked, fetch referrer's rate: `db.getReferrerRate(referrerWallet, defaultRateBps)`\n3. Calculate earnings:\n   - `feeLamports = floor((wagerLamports * feeBps) / 10_000)`\n   - `referrerEarnedLamports = floor((feeLamports * referrerRateBps) / 10_000)`\n   - `refereeRebateLamports = floor((feeLamports * 1000) / 10_000)` (fixed 10% for v1)\n4. Insert earning row: `db.insertReferralEarning({...})`\n\n---\n\n## 7. Truncate/Cleanup Isolation Pattern\n\nThe test uses TRUNCATE with CASCADE and RESTART IDENTITY:\n\n```sql\nTRUNCATE referral_codes, referral_links, referral_earnings, referral_claims, \n  referral_kol_rates, event_queue RESTART IDENTITY CASCADE\n```\n\n**Key behaviors**:\n- Deletes all rows in all 5 referral tables + event queue\n- Resets all SERIAL sequences (id fields) back to 1\n- CASCADE honors foreign key constraints (though these tables don't have cross-table FKs)\n- Runs **before each test** (`beforeEach`), ensuring clean state\n- Transaction-safe — rolled back if test fails\n\n---\n\n## File Paths (Absolute)\n\n1. **Test Suite**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/__tests__/referral-routes.test.ts`\n2. **Database Client**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts`\n3. **Routes Handler**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/routes/referral.ts`\n4. **Settlement Integration**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts`\n5. **Referral Migration**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/migrations/011_referral.sql`\n6. **Event Queue Migration**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/migrations/010_event_queue.sql`"}],"totalDurationMs":93578,"totalTokens":73633,"totalToolUseCount":21,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":639,"cache_read_input_tokens":69123,"output_tokens":3871,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":639},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
